sql: SELECT c_nation, s_nation, d_year, SUM(lo_revenue) AS lo_revenue FROM ssb.p_lineorder LEFT JOIN ssb.dates ON lo_orderdate = d_datekey LEFT JOIN ssb.customer ON lo_custkey = c_custkey LEFT JOIN ssb.supplier ON lo_suppkey = s_suppkey WHERE c_region = 'ASIA' AND s_region = 'ASIA' AND d_year >= 1992 AND d_year <= 1997 GROUP BY c_nation, s_nation, d_year ORDER BY d_year ASC, lo_revenue DESC
